==English==
===Noun===
'''[[Easter]] [[egg]]''' (''plural:'' '''Easter eggs''')

#A [[dye]]d or [[decorate]]d egg, [[traditionally]] associated with Easter.
#A [[chocolate]] [[confection]] in the shape of an egg, sometimes with [[chocolate]]s or [[sweet]]s inside.
#{{computing}} An [[undocumented]] [[function]] [[hidden]] in a [[program]], typically [[trigger]]ed by a particular sequence or combination of [[keystroke]]s, such as one that displays a list of the program's [[developer]]s.

